00:09:39.500 --> 00:09:41.390
who's the other
character, and Ranjana,

00:09:41.390 --> 00:09:47.480
are people who haven't spent any
copious amount of time thinking

00:09:47.480 --> 00:09:49.670
about, again, what agency
they have in the world,

00:09:49.670 --> 00:09:51.950
